{"id":41457,"title":"[Prognostication of efficacy of simultant laparoscopic operations in accordance to the risk estimation scale, and the method of establishing of indications and contraindications].","abstract":"Experience of surgical treatment was summarized and its results were analyzed in patients, suffering biliary calculous disease, coexistent with other surgical diseases of abdominal organs. Main aspects of diagnosis and prognosis for efficacy of simultant operations were presented, and there were also adduced the method of prognosis of the operative treatment results in such patients, the proposed principle of determination of indications and contraindications for performance of simultant laparoscopic operations, a scale of the risk estimation for performance of such operative interventions.","date":"2014-06-13","categories":"Digestive System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24923116","annotations":[{"name":"Disease","weight":0.797998,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Prognosis","weight":0.762559,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prognosis"},{"name":"Contraindication","weight":0.758091,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Contraindication"},{"name":"Diagnosis","weight":0.756683,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diagnosis"},{"name":"Abdomen","weight":0.752214,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abdomen"},{"name":"Organ (anatomy)","weight":0.748635,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Organ_(anatomy)"},{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.689906,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Laparoscopic surgery","weight":0.621643,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laparoscopic_surgery"},{"name":"Efficacy","weight":0.594769,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Efficacy"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.542761,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Bile